## Description
The `ProgressBar` component attaches a `scroll` event listener even on routes where it returns `null` (non-`/sem*` routes).

In `app/components/ProgressBar.tsx`, the scroll listener is registered inside `useEffect` before the component conditionally exits:

```tsx
useEffect(() => {
  window.addEventListener('scroll', handleScroll);

  return () => {
    window.removeEventListener('scroll', handleScroll);
  };
}, [pathname]);

if (!pathname.startsWith('/sem')) {
  return null;
}
